MANAMA, Bahrain, January 9, 2022/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The Kingdom of Bahrain welcomes the dialogue between the Sudanese parties and stresses its support for reviving the political process in brotherly Sudan, which would achieve security, peace, unity and stability of Sudan.

It also notes the constructive role played by the United Nations in this regard and the efforts exerted by the United Nations Integrated Transition Assistance Mission in Sudan (UNITAMS), to hold political consultations among all components, affirming the solidarity of Bahrain and its full support for Sudan to achieve the aspirations of its brotherly people for stability, peace and development.